msgstr "Používatelia najprv kupujú kryptomenu, potom ju odosielajú vám"

msgid ""
"MoonPay lets users buy crypto with credit card directly to THEIR wallet, "
"then they send it to you. Higher fees but very simple for users."
msgstr ""
"MoonPay umožňuje používateľom nakupovať kryptomenu kreditnou kartou priamo "
