msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Platby Stripe Crypto (USDC) sú k dispozícii IBA pre americké podniky. Ak nie"
" ste v USA, Stripe akceptuje len platby kreditnou kartou na váš Stripe účet "
"(nie priamo na kryptomenu)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Ak ste v USA, môžete Stripe použiť na priamy príjem kryptomien. Ak ste mimo,"
" zvážte NOWPayments alebo CoinGate pre priamy výplat kryptomien."

